<article class="row hentry post-269032 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-donald-trump tag-health-care tag-matt-gaetz tag-mick-mulvaney tag-public-health tag-republicans section-environment-and-health primary_topic-health" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
